or the sum of thermal and turbulent+magnetic\Upsilon_{\rm th} = 267{\rm km/s} \left(\frac{P_{\rm DE}/k_B}{10^4 {\rm cm^{-3}\,K}}\right)^{-0.506}\Upsilon_{\rm turb+mag} = 1.5*370{\rm km/s} \left(\frac{P_{\rm DE}/k_B}{10^4 {\rm cm^{-3}\,K}}\right)^{-0.060}

where we assume that the magnetic contribution is 50% of the turbulent.

